import React from "react"; import { useState, useEffect } from "react"; function RiskCalculator(){ const [feePercentage, setFeePercentage] = useState(''); const [expectedBill, setExpectedBill] = useState('') let total; useEffect(()=> { total = ({expectedBill} * ({feePercentage}/100)); },); return( <>
setFeePercentage(event.target.value)} >
setExpectedBill(event.target.value)} >
{total} ); }; export default RiskCalculator;
